channel.title: Removing World Object
channel.description: Hello, i am working on a new source and i need to remove an object or 2. How do i remove these objects, They're not in my GlobalOjbect's Or DeleteThatObject. Where would i find the objects that you dont put in but are just there. As in tables and walls or grass or somthing. iv seen alot of servers that have done that.

Where would i find the objects that you dont put in but are just there. As in tables and walls or grass or somthing. iv seen alot of servers that have done that.
